<div class="NavContent" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/God_in_Judaism" title="God in Judaism">God in Judaism</a> (<a href="/wiki/Names_of_God_in_Judaism" title="Names of God in Judaism">Names</a>)<br />
<a href="/wiki/Jewish_principles_of_faith" title="Jewish principles of faith">Principles of faith</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mitzvah" title="Mitzvah">Mitzvot</a> (<a href="/wiki/613_Mitzvot" title="613 Mitzvot">613</a>)<br />
